
ENTITY RecoveryBot
STATE Active
ENERGY 100
REPUTATION 0

BEHAVIOR
  IF ENERGY < 30 THEN STATE Recovery
  IF STATE == Recovery THEN ENERGY + 15
  IF ENERGY > 80 THEN STATE Active
END

EXECUTE
  IF STATE == Active THEN DataCollector
  IF STATE == Recovery THEN Monitor
END

INTENT "Test energy restoration mechanics"
MODE Testing
